  <%- include("./partials/nav") %>

  <main class="about">
    <div class="about__container">
      <h1 class="about__title">About Zipply</h1>
      <p class="about__intro">
        <strong>Zipply</strong> is a powerful and modern <span>URL Shortener</span> and <span>Barcode/QR Code Generator</span> built for simplicity, performance, and utility.
      </p>

      <p>
        It was crafted with ❤️ by <strong>Aman Show</strong>, using a full-stack approach with cutting-edge web technologies like <strong>Node.js</strong>, <strong>Express</strong>, <strong>MongoDB</strong>, <strong>JWT Authentication</strong>, and <strong>Bootstrap</strong> for design.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether you want to trim long links, generate scannable QR codes, or track link analytics—Zipply is designed to help you do it all with speed and reliability.
      </p>

      <h2 class="about__subheading">Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul class="about__tech-list">
        <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose</li>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> EJS, Bootstrap, Custom CSS</li>
        <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> JSON Web Tokens (JWT)</li>
        <li><strong>Extras:</strong> Clipboard copy, QR Code generation, Click tracking</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="about__end">Zipply is fast, free, and made with care. Start shortening and sharing smarter — today!</p>
    </div>
  </main>

